This directory contains code used only stochastic FTS calculations
using a partial-saddle point approximation using a GPU accelerator.

Subdirectories:
---------------

analyzer/      - data analysis classes (for on-the-fly or postprocessing)
brownian/      - Brownian dynamics FTS algorithms
compressor/    - algorithms to iteratively find a partial saddle point
montecarlo/    - Monte Carlo FTS algorithms
perturbation/  - perturbations of the Hamiltonian (e.g., Einstein crystal)
ramp/          - continuous parameter ramp during simulation
simulator/     - Simulator base class and factory, class SimState
trajectory/    - reading field trajectory files (postprocessing)

C++/CUDA source files:
----------------------

VecOpFts.*     - GPU vector operations needed for FTS simulations

Makefile and makefile fragments:
--------------------------------

makefile      - makefile for rpg/fts directory tree
sources.mk    - list of source files in rpg/fts (makefile fragment)

Doxygen documentation files:
----------------------------

fts.mod       - definition of the Rpg_Fts_Module doxygen topic module

